  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Doraemon: Yume Dorobou to 7-nin no Gozans is a 1993 platformer by Sega for the Sega Mega Drive tying into the Doraemon media franchise.\n\nB jumps. C shoots your gun, which stuns enemies so you can safely jump on them and use them as platforms. The longer you hold C, the more powerful your shots get; sufficiently powerful shots can destroy enemies.",
